            <fr:title text="noetherian space">noetherian space</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
  A space is <html:strong>noetherian</html:strong> if every descending chain of closeds, or equivalently every ascending chain of opens stabilizes. In other words, the partial order of closeds is well-founded.
</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
